{
    "description_long": "This grave yard is enclosed by a tall, spiked wrought iron fence with stone pillars at regular intervals, creating a foreboding perimeter. Inside, the ground is covered with patches of grass and stone walkways, leading to a central domed mausoleum supported by four columns. Several gravestones of varying shapes and sizes are scattered throughout, some upright and others leaning, with a few stone statues and benches adding to the somber atmosphere. Two smaller stone buildings, resembling chapels or crypts, are positioned at the rear corners, each with steeply pitched roofs and arched doorways. The entrance is marked by a prominent gate flanked by stone pillars, and the entire area is meticulously organized, with clear paths and defined sections. The overall color palette is dominated by shades of gray and green, giving the scene a weathered, aged appearance.",
    "description": "A fenced grave yard with a central domed mausoleum, scattered gravestones, two small stone buildings, and a prominent iron gate, all set on a grassy stone-covered ground.",
